.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-FEE-REVENUE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-fee-revenue \- summarise routing fee revenue
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-fee-revenue
.RB [ --days
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Aggregates routing fee revenue from forwarded payments over the last
.I N
days (default: 7).
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"period_days":N,"count":N,"earned_msat":N,"failed_count":N,"since_ts":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-api-forward-stats (1),
.BR lightning-node-health (1)
